&lt;li&gt;Experience with Kubernetes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with GCP cloud services, including GKE and Anthos&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Gitlab and especially Gitlab CI/CD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ArgoCD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with service-mesh technologies: Istio, Linkerd, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide on-call support to NCBI&#39;s internal developers and other staff.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Educational Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS degree in a STEM field, or equivalent experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer-focused, team-oriented disposition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good systems debugging skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with the Linux environment or UNIX CLI&lt;/li&gt;
