&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;GitLab CI pipeline configuration, templates, and components to build a standardized ecosystem for developers across the organization to use for their applications, in many languages, from C++ to Scala, Kotlin, and Python.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python applications, scripts, and libraries to provide interfaces for DevOps and customer tools to manage builds, deployments, and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Kubernetes configuration templates using the YTT templating language to create and maintain customizable patterns for consistent deployments across application teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Debugging deployments on Kubernetes distributions like Openshift and Anthos and using plugins like ArgoCD, Istio, and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Documentation knowledge bases for each component project and the DevEx platform as a whole, in READMEs and on Confluence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading smaller projects within the DevEx teams to add new capabilities to the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
