&lt;h2 class=&quot;iCIMS_InfoMsg iCIMS_InfoField_Job&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: large;&quot;&gt;Overview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Black Canyon Consulting (BCC) is a premium provider for life sciences, project and program management. We are searching for a Product Manager&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;to support our work with a renowned federal agency where you will help drive modernization in one of the world’s largest data repositories.&amp;nbsp;We are looking for full-time candidates currently residing in the United States. This position is available for remote work.&lt;/p&gt;
