&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dynamic Product Manager who will play a vital role in the success of the IT/Product Modernization for one of the largest public repositories of high-throughput data sequencing. The ideal candidate will guide product success, define vision, and prioritize government customer requirements. You will collaborate to meet contract deliverables and ensure customer satisfaction. In this role, you will work 50% with a Product Team and 50% with the Customer Experience/Stakeholder Engagement team. Working with the Product Team, you will ensure continued alignment of the software Product with the overall Product Modernization roadmap and provide transparent communication and management of the Product Roadmap. As part of the Customer Experience/Stakeholder Engagement team, you will conduct customer outreach, analyze market trends, conduct competitive analysis, and develop strategies to increase SRA platform usage. Strong leadership, excellent communication, and understanding of government clients are essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in being a part of an organization that operates within the intersection of technology and health, please apply today!&lt;/p&gt;
